 id=\"note17a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.26?lang=por#p26\">1 Né. 22:26</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/6.15?lang=por#p15\">3 Né. 6:15</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"20\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note20a\" data-full-marker=\"20a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124172053\" id=\"note20a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/humble-humility?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Humildade, Humilde, Humilhar</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note20b\" data-full-marker=\"20b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124172054\" id=\"note20b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.35?lang=por#p35\">1 Né. 17:35</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"23\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note23a\" data-full-marker=\"23a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124172055\" id=\"note23a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.45?lang=por#p45\">D&amp;C 42:45</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"24\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note24a\" data-full-marker=\"24a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124172056\" id=\"note24a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/46.12?lang=por#p12\">Al. 46:12</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note24b\" data-full-marker=\"24b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124172057\" id=\"note24b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/apostasy?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Apostasia</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","footnotes":{"note5a":{"id":"note5a","marker":"5a","pid":"124172017","context":"capitães-chefes","text":"<p data-aid=\"124172040\" id=\"note5a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/43.6?lang=por#p6\">Al. 43:6</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/4